h3. _YES_,

You can build a decent presentation outside of a cubersome, difficult to use, all bells and whistles, no fun, presentation software suite!
~~
Skiny slides is a simple minimalistic presentation software that focus on content and not on superficial effects!

*Use the cursor to move through this presentation*
~~
h1. Plain text format loves you!

No more proprietary format to hold your data!
~~
h1. Advantages

* Easy to compare presentations
* Easy to type with the textile markup language
* Easy to paste code or integrate other plain format text
~~
h1. About Textile

Textile is a human to computer translator that lets you format your code in an easy way. 
~~
h1. Code!

Copy and paste code directly into your slide! Skiny slides uses the javascript highliting library "shjs":http://shjs.sourceforge.net/. Just indicate the highlighter for your code and shjs takes care of it.
~~
<pre class="sh_python">
class You(object):
  def can_paste(self, ):
    code = Code()
    code.directly_into("skiny slides")

  def feels_good(self, ):
    print "and awesome ;-)" 
</pre>

Yes! It looks great!
